"Set Colorscheme
colorscheme desert
set term=xterm-256color "helps with PuTTY

"Tabs and Spaces for Drupal Standards
set number
set expandtab
set tabstop=2
set shiftwidth=2
set softtabstop=2
set autoindent
set smartindent

"User Interface Settings
syntax on
set cursorline " highlight current line
set wildmenu " visial autocomplete for command menu
set lazyredraw " redraw only wnen we need to
set showmatch " hightlight matching

"Search
set incsearch
set hlsearch

"Keymapping
map <C-r> :Rex<cr>

"Stuff to make Vim work better with macOS terminal
set clipboard=unnamed
set backspace=2
